Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gust of wind came...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thermos fell over...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sandwiches were all dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just smiled sadly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.48,0:00:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want one too, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.72,0:01:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can t get through to Mr. Verdeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, his wife just gave birth, so he's probably\Nstill at the maternity center.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've heard about you, Miss Eva Heinemann.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, feel free to tell me anything you'd like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The testimony to prove Tenma's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. We're very grateful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what hotel are you staying at right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Got it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head over there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:03.70,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(226,200)\pos(363,355)}Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With timing like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll just go around me and keep driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car comes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This timing should be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.52,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to marry me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swear to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll swear to anything you want today, Helene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then kiss me, Gustav.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue this in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used my drugs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last of my stash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder your nose is running, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out here practicing for my job while\Nyou're in here snorting my stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What job? It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you're doing is lying in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I mess up even a little, I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be killed instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:06:00.04,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that was just an example...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still some things I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta have lots of kids with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to make a whole soccer team with our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so wonderful, Gustav.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be getting a load of cash from the job I'm about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make my dream come true, right, Helene?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have them! I'll have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have as many babies as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you, now is not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want to make babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be patient for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for a "Detective Forster" rerun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I jump out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I jump out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I jump out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of killing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your former fiancee...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such nice weather, yet I'm stuck in a car like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this damn serial killer, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm so unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this gloomy little prison van...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on your way to some dank detention facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get to hear plenty of stories about the twelve\Nescapes of the master escapee, Gunther Milch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, which should I start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one about how I escaped from\NKreiner Prison is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. I'm just bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you for the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 9:32.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were out in the free world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd almost be time for a rerun\Nof "Detective Forster" on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever watch that show?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take care of this little job real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just watch me work from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to shoot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just gonna use it to scare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want our kids to have murderers for parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shoot anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even stop using drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Helene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've really decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna live honestly from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do jobs where I have to\Nwave a gun around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing good comes from waving around things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! This feels so great, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you from the bottom of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hit someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.93,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... hit someone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... hit him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.10,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me? Sit down, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan... failed, Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I taught Gustav the timing and\Nacting over and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end, nobody can do it as well as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to pass out on the road like he was sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so he could stop the oncoming car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really bad, so you should've just\Navoided him and kept going...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why did you have to go and hit him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get what you're saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go check and see if it's someone you know or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Gustav...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helene...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is he still breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me, but we have a doctor right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I have done this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've totally failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should tell him to cover it up in the report...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we cover up something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the keys to the handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the keys to the handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like anything to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In our next story...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}fire struck a large shopping mall in Dortmund today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks to the employees triggering the fire alarm,\Nthe blaze was brought under control...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but two stores were completely lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There have been no reported injuries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.02,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I'd talk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The testimony to prove Tenma's innocence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Got it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll head over there right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please wait in the hotel lobby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do by setting that man free?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At 10 o'clock this morning, in a suburb\Nof D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf, Erkrath...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}two prisoners who were being transported to the Hilden\NDetention Facility escaped from police custody.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No details have been reported, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the two fugitives who escaped were...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gunther Milch, arrested for armored car robbery...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the serial killer, Kenzou Tenma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The police have been deployed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and are now tracking down the two fugitives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.46,0:15:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Verdeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I heard the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you have to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I was about to prove your innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's no use asking me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand his motives either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:15:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's just head over to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the truth is, there's something\Nthat I have to take care of first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Yes. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must both deal with the current situation calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That voice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we have to get the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That voice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's exactly as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That voice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.91,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as much as we can. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not... my cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that man's smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roberto was just in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helene, he's not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hit his head, and he's not bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's what they call a brain hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to change cars at the path through\Nthe forest up ahead, like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav is just a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave him in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to change cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cops have seen this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll find us in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can get him to a hospital soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a chance he can be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, your quick-wittedness saved my\Nescape plan when it was about to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But from now on, you're going to listen to the pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for him, but we'll leave Gustav at\Nthe path through the forest up ahead and--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep driving to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisler Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have the best equipment\Nand staff in D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the hospital I worked at!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The main entrance to the hospital is just ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you reach the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell them to give this letter to Dr. Wagner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It contains a detailed description of the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gustav won't die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up as long as he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we stick around here any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like we'll be asking to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better stick with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a complete amateur at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life of a woman I know is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get to her as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:21:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to tell me that's why you escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want women, just come with me to Tunisia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep with as many of\Nthe best women as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't really killed anyone, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shot one person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as that one goes, you're completely innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.83,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've got a real criminal record now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're now officially a fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.92,0:21:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet up in Tunisia someday, fugitive to fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.18,0:21:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.91,0:22:31.08,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:44.51,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.47,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:23:01.15,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:26.01,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:34.43,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:36.89,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
